SUMMARY:Configure new laptop: Neo
DESCRIPTION:1. ☒ Install homebrew\n   1. ☑ Install hledger\n   2. ☐ Configu
 re hledger\n2. ☒ Install other essential apps/software\n   1. ☒ Syncthing\
 n      1. ☒ Configure Syncthing\, launch on startup/login\n   2. ☑ Firefox
 \n   3. ☑ MacVim\n   4. ☑ Claude\n   5. ☑ Quicksilver\, launch on startup/
 login\n   6. ☐ Emacs railwaycat\n      1. ☐ Install missing packages (only
  a few)\n3. ☑ Setup eduroam\n4. ☒ Install apps/software to match "old" dev
 ice\n   1. ☐ +pdftk+\, use Preview instead\n   2. ☑ Zoom\n   3. ☒ OneDrive
 \n      1. Setup paths correctly?\n   4. ☐ Inkscape\n   5. ☐ GIMP\n   6. ☐
  ApE\n   7. ☐ Fiji\n5. ☒ Helper apps\n   1. ☐ Rectangle\n   2. ☐ BetterDis
 play: DCC issue via HDMI\n   3. ☐ HazeOver\n   4. ☑ PDF Viewer\n   5. ☐ Sk
 im (PDF)\n   6. ☑ Goodnotes\n6. LaTeX\n   1. ☐ MacTeX
CATEGORIES:Vida
SEQUENCE:1
PRIORITY:5
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
END:VTODO
